body: This migrates from `node-ffi` to `node-ffi-napi`, as the former seems unmaintained and broken on recent node versions. The work for that is done by @Pigpog . This PR includes the following `node-ffi-napi` PR to, well, fix it so that it is not crashing on c callbacks: https://github.com/node-ffi-napi/node-ffi-napi/pull/56 Fixes #17 --- This change isâ€‚[](https://reviewable.io/reviews/toktok/js-toxcore-c/18)
